                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10166" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0350</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">125 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">教育筑基，产业赋能:化销华南书写乡村振兴“石化答卷”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">无</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">邹立凯，宋丽红，杜友德</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">汕头大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国石化化工销售华南分公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">化学工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">党群部门/思想政治工作部门/企业文化部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">乡村振兴；教育帮扶；产业造血；生态共建；国企社会责任；国企专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Rural revitalization;Education assistance;Industrial blood production; Ecological co-construction; Social responsibility of state-owned enterprises</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国石化化工销售华南分公司（化销华南）积极响应国家乡村振兴战略，以广东省雷州市松竹镇八龙村为帮扶对象，探索“教育筑基、产业造血、生态共建”的乡村振兴模式。通过精准调研，化销华南针对八龙村集体经济薄弱、教育设施落后、资源闲置等问题，实施“三步走”战略：联合政府提供政策支持，导入企业资源盘活物流与农产品销售，建立村民自治机制。教育方面，发起“圆心愿”行动，个性化满足留守儿童需求，改造校舍并引入多媒体教学资源，小学升学率提升至98%；产业方面，成立运输合作社整合资源，打造“松竹香米”品牌，通过石化渠道实现溢价超30%，村集体收入从零增长至2023年的30万元；生态方面，推进污水治理工程、塑料分类循环利用及绿色农业项目，改善人居环境并提升资源利用效率。截至2025年，累计投入帮扶资金超200万元，惠及村民千余人，八龙村从“空心村”蜕变为“示范村”，形成可复制的乡村振兴实践经验。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Sinopec Chemical Sales South China Branch focuses on Bailong Village in Songzhu Town, Leizhou City, Guangdong Province, and supports rural revitalization through the &quot;education revitalization, industrial hematopoiesis and ecological co construction&quot; model. In response to the problems of lagging education, weak collective economy, and idle resources in the village, targeted measures have been taken to promote education in southern China. In terms of education, the &quot;Central Aspiration&quot; action has been launched to improve teaching facilities, introduce the &quot;Petrochemical Cloud Classroom&quot; to enhance education quality, and increase the primary school enrollment rate to 98%; In terms of industry, a transportation cooperative was established to integrate logistics resources, create the &quot;Songzhu Fragrant Rice&quot; brand, and promote it through petrochemical channels. The collective economic income of the village increased from scratch to over 300000 yuan; In terms of ecology, we will promote sewage treatment, plastic classification and utilization, and green agriculture projects to improve the living environment and achieve resource recycling. By 2025, a total investment of over 2 million yuan has been made, benefiting over a thousand villagers and exploring a sustainable development path that involves collaboration between the government, enterprises, and villagers.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业社会责任》、《商业伦理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业社会责任；乡村振兴；利益相关者理论；价值共创理论；可持续发展理念</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-12</td>
                            </tr>
